The Invisible Burden of Violence Against Girls and Young Women in Mexico: 1990 
to 2015.

Romero Mendoza MP(1), Gómez-Dantes H(2), Manríquez Montiel Q(1), Saldívar 
Hernández GJ(1), Campuzano Rincón JC(2), Lozano R(2)(3), Medina-Mora Icaza 
