An examination of user costs in relation to smokers using a cessation service 
based in the UK.

Walker N(1), Yang Y(2), Kiparoglou V(1)(3), Pokhrel S(4), Robinson H(5), van 
Woerden H(6)(7).

Author information:
(1)NIHR Oxford Biomedical Research Centre, Churchill Hospital, Old Road, 
